    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, boasting a flawless exterior profile complemented by an interior that retains its original luster and integrity. A rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a specimen of unparalleled quality and mechanical excellence.",
      "price": 48950.0,
