      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 high-revving straight-six with its signature individual throttle bodies. This specimen boasts a structurally sound subframe and recently addressed rod bearings, ensuring long-term mechanical integrity. The double VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to maintain peak variable valve timing performance. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut, riding on staggered OEM forged wheels, while the interior displays no bolster wear or pixel degradation. A mechanically peerless example for the discerning collector seeking a visceral, analog driving experience.",
